				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Famitracker is just a particular sound engine. Other sound engine will have their own terminology to describe what FT calls &quot;instrument&quot; or &quot;effect&quot;, or will use something that has no direct equivalent to FT.<br /><br />Think of it like a scroll engine or a sprite engine - there's no &quot;one way&quot; to do it.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

